title: For Sale/Trade:  VZ2008 w/accessories & 5 mags
postcontent:
Up for sale/trade is a nice VZ2008. Comes with 5 mags (4 which are near brand new), sling, bayonet/scabbard, cleaning kit, and 4 cell magazine pouch. It has the side folding stock with paracord wrapped around to give a bit of cheek weld. Never had a malfunction with it. 

If you don't know about VZ2008s, they are a copy of VZ58s which is a Czech design with a few differences being its NOT Full Auto and the barrel is slightly longer so its over 16ins. Its a milled receiver with a striker fire design and gas system similar to the SKS. The magazines have a Bolt-Hold Open feature and the bolt stays back once the magazine is empty. VZ58s are completely different from the AK family except for the caliber, 7.62x39. You can also load the magazine via stripper clips since the bolt has a notch which is really neat. 

I hope I answered some question but aside that price is 550 OBO.

I bought this one brand new 3 weeks ago from the The Sportsman gun shop in concord nc.
First of all.....I have shot pistol competition in different diciplines over the last 30 yrs.....mostly bullseye...PPC and metallic silhouette. ...I bought this to shoot IDPA or maybe an occasional glock match. Out of the box.....best I could get were 3" groups at 25 yds....totally unacceptable for a bullseye shooter. So I ordered a barsto match barrel $230......and a vanek competition drop in trigger $165....and finished up with a set of warren tactical competition target steel sight......The results were astonishing.......will shoot less than 1" @ 25yds and  2 1/2" @ 50 yds with Winchester white box 115gr.......I love what this pistol is capable of .......however....my daughter got married last weekend and put a huge dent in my finances...so I have decided to part ways with awesome pistol. Included is everything that came with the pistol....and everything that was added....I even purchased a blade tec comp holster that has never been opened....that i will include with the deal.    Price is $780   if interested seven o four 32 two 52 one 9.....Jody
